## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="cc701-143">По умолчанию этому свойству присваивается значение `System.String.Empty`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cc701-143">The default value of this property is `System.String.Empty`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cc701-144">Приложения могут полностью изменить значение <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cc701-144">Applications are free to completely change the value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cc701-145">Сброс значения <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A> не изменится значение <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextOffset%2A> и <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextLength%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cc701-145">Resetting the value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A> will not change the value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextOffset%2A> and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextLength%2A>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
